f3;square;f3;type;Inaccuracy;persistent;true]} (22. g3) 22... Rae8 23. Qd3 Re7
24. g3 {Hope chess. Planning to trap the bishop.} 24... Rfe8 25. Kg2 {A
defensive move, but I changed my mind and offered a draw instead. A cowardly
