g3;square;g3;type;Mistake;persistent;true] A terrible move apparently, loses
instantly.} 26... Qxg3+ 27. Kh1 Qh3+ 28. Kg1 Qg3+ 29. Kh1 Re2 30. Rg5 Rh2+ 31.
Nxh2) 1/2-1/2

