Ne2 {[%c_effect f5;square;f5;type;Winner;animated;true] Robbert flags before he
can make this move. I apologise, he shakes hands and walks away quickly. He's
understandably upset, since all 3 results are still possible and he really
should've just played anything. Both of us were still writing down moves even
with under 10 seconds on the clock, which was really unnecessary.} 0-1

